user.biography: Family of five on a mission to help feed children. For every ethically produced, hand-knit doll sold, we provide 10 meals to children in need.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by cuddle+kind on August 31, 2021 tagging @ryleeandcru. May be an image of 1 person, child and indoor.

node.text:
One, two, three, four, could I love you any more?💞 We spend a lot of time designing each of our hand-knit dolls with our favourite modern colours and whimsical heirloom quality details, making them perfect companions for stylish little ones with kind hearts. ⁠
⁠
Which hand-knit dolls does your little one have in their collection?💕⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #handmadewithlove #babyanimals #1babyanimalequals5meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.text:
The cutest koala hug we ever did see!🐨 Quinn the koala is lovingly handcrafted to be exceptionally cuddly: his ears are knit with a special fuzzy yarn little ones absolutely love. It makes a little koal-ity time even sweeter.💕⁠
⁠
{📸: @sierralmiller } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by cuddle+kind on August 29, 2021 tagging @briarbaby, @shoplovedua, @blossomandpear, and @edemasellis.

node.text:
Congratulations, mama!✨ Lucas the llama’s favourite thing is making new friends (and making them laugh)! He is looking forward to making your little one giggle with his lla-mazing jokes as soon as they meet. ⁠
⁠
If you’re expecting, don’t forget to tag #MilestonesForMeals in your little one’s milestone photos! We want to help them spread kindness from day one, so we donate an extra meal to children in need for every milestone photo with their cuddle+kind doll.💖⁠
⁠
{📸: @edemasellis } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.text:
Slow Saturday naps.💤 We can’t get enough of these dreamy neutrals or that sweet hand on Lucy the lamb’s shoulder! This adorable image is giving us all the early fall vibes.✨⁠
⁠
{📸: @rebecca.zaffina } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by cuddle+kind on August 27, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, baby and people standing.

node.text:
Smiles as bright as the stars.⭐ Luna the mermaid believes that following your dreams is the bravest thing you can do. She would love to be your little one’s BFF, encouraging them to show the world just how extraordinary they can be! ⁠
⁠
If you’ve never seen her up close, she has the dreamiest heirloom details, like the sparkly crocheted starfish in her hair, and flowing seafoam tassel top. ⁠
⁠
She’s out of stock right now, so make sure to sign up for back in stock notifications on her product page and we’ll be sure to let you know when she’s available again!✨⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by cuddle+kind on August 26, 2021 tagging @littleunicornofficial, and @mushie.

node.text:
We can’t stand the cuteness! Baby kitten and flamingo feel right at home with all these natural, thoughtful, organic baby gifts. ⁠
⁠
We poured a tremendous amount of love, care and attention into designing our baby animals, from crafting their beautifully detailed designs to selecting only the finest natural cotton yarns. Our Baby Animal Collection makes a wonderful gift for the newborn little ones in your life.✨⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #handmadewithlove #babyanimals #1babyanimalequals5meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.text:
A purr-fect pair.💕 Dylan the kitten is very content to be twinning with this little darling. Like all our hand-knit dolls, he has a signature 1 doll = 10 meals wristband to remind you of the good you did with your purchase. We love that children can have a connection with the children they help feed through their own favourite doll.🍲⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #handmadewithlove #babyanimals #1babyanimalequals5meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

Hand-knit perfection.💕 Don’t these soft colours remind you of a dreamy sunrise? ⁠
⁠
We love creating our dolls in modern, gorgeous colours that can complement your little one’s outfits. These darling dolls would be the perfect companion for stylish little ones with kind hearts.✨⁠

node.text:
Five months of friendship, a lifetime to go.✨ This sweet milestone photo has us absolutely squealing! It’s just what we needed to brighten our day. ⁠
⁠
Did you know that when you post a monthly milestone photo of your little one with their cuddle+kind doll and tag #MilestonesForMeals, we’ll donate a meal to children in need? We are always committed to helping you spread kindness by giving as much as we can. Thank you for participating!💕⁠
⁠
{📸: @charlinjanene } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

After every storm, comes a rainbow.🌈 The sun may rise and set each day, but we know that love lives in the heart forever. On National Rainbow Baby Day, Ella the unicorn wishes you all the comfort and joy that life can hold.⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #NationalRainbowBabyDay #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.text:
In a world of clouds, be somebody’s sunshine.☀️ This little one is already lighting up the world with that sweet smile. And, every doll in her collection has provided 10 meals to children in need!⁠
⁠
We guarantee that every hand-knit character you collect will be loved, and will make a positive impact on the world: providing artisans in Peru with fair trade income and making a difference for children facing hunger around the world.💛⁠
⁠
{📸: @kashiapalmer } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.text:
Oh, darling little deers!💚 Elliott the fawn feels so lucky to be this little one’s forever friend. Can you tell by that look of sweet admiration? ⁠
⁠
Elliott, like all our dolls, is lovingly handcrafted with naturally dyed cotton yarn that is exceptionally soft on the skin. Seeing these quiet moments make our heart melt, and remind us why we do what we do! 💕⁠
⁠
{📸: @helloroxytru } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade
